type: software
title: "Masakhane Playbook: A Practical Guide for Building NLP Systems for African Languages"
abstract: >
  A community-driven, open guide for building, evaluating, and deploying
  natural language processing systems for African languages. Covers dataset
  design, annotation, model training, evaluation, deployment, and ethics.
